"almost plaintext"

Built to look like those IETF RFCs, but with some simple
CSS styles to make it easier to read. The goal was to add
enough css to make it responsive for mobile reading

Features:
- Hugo to get a better editing experience w/ Markdown
- max width 60ch with 1ch padding
- center the content on the page
- fancy ordered list decoration with proper margins
- make the content look nearly the same in my editor
- preflight.css file copied from tailwind to reset styles
- Hugo template to deal with opengraph meta tags